    <div class="hero-simple" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7)), url('https://static-asset.amac.us/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/10103648/homes.jpg');">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Your Local, Family-Owned Agency</h1>
            <p>Since 1979, we've built our reputation on one simple promise: <strong>We work for you.</strong></p>
        </div>
