    <section class="section-padding mission-area">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="mission-box">
                <h2>Our Mission: <span id="typing-text"></span></h2>
                <div class="mission-description">
                    <p>It is our pleasure to introduce you to Hometown Insurance – one of New York State's leading Independent Insurance Agencies. Our commitment is to serve you with the highest degree of professionalism. You can expect us to utilize our extensive knowledge and experience to act as your personal insurance advisers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="about-grid">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h2>Rooted in Our Community</h2>
                    <p>Welcome to Hometown Insurance, one of New York State's leading independent insurance agencies. Proudly serving individuals, families, and businesses since 1979, we provide customized home insurance, auto insurance, business insurance, and specialty coverage solutions throughout Long Island and New York State.</p>
                    <br>
                    <p>While our agency has grown over the years, our core values remain the same. We continue to uphold the traditions established by our founders and the high standards of service and professionalism that our clients have trusted for generations.</p>
                    <br>
                    <p>Our formula for success is simple: we treat our neighbors like family. As an independent agency, our team works as your personal insurance advisors—using our experience to help you find the right home, auto, or business insurance coverage at the most competitive price.</p>
                    <br>
                    <a href="tel:6315890100" class="btn btn-red">Give Us a Call Today</a>
                </div>
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="https://static-asset.amac.us/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/10142752/family-kite.jpg" alt="Hometown Family" class="about-img">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
